flex.tools.debugger.cli

Class BreakAction

  • java.lang.Object
    • flex.tools.debugger.cli.BreakAction

  • public class BreakAction
extends Object
    An object that relates a CLI debugger breakpoint with an associated set of CLI commands to perform. A breakpoint can be enabled or disabled. It can be set such that it disabled or deletes itself after being hit N times.
